dataStructure

Interface graph

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DGraph

    public interface graph
    This interface represents a directional weighted graph. The interface has a road-system or communication network in mind - and should support a large number of nodes (over 100,000). The implementation should be based on an efficient compact representation (should NOT be based on a n*n matrix).
